{
  "stem": "17761.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And Jews stood around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I don't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But suddenly my father said to me like this, [NON-ENGLISH] We say kaddish, we say [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Know But on [NON-ENGLISH], which is the day afterwards, we dance also with the Torah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we went back to the place where we had this little Torah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "From nowhere we got some table.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we danced with the Torah in this scenery, in this-- on this background, in these chaos.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was like a struggle to maintain human dignity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was a struggle to maintain the relation with our past.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was a struggle to be-- to remain just human beings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I don't know where from my father took this strength.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I just know now-- later is so many years, I can appreciate what he did then to us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was a struggle for survival, for moral survival, let-- let alone the physical survival.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The day after was [NON-ENGLISH] and then was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "My father did all he could and he succeeded that we shouldn't be moved over Dniester Dmn during the holidays.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "So we stayed in this place until after [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all dispersed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were hundreds and thousands of people around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- there was no counting in that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody was for himself to keep this little family together that we shouldn't lose each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had some food we brought with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is there any degree lower than zero?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sanitation, eh, that's-- we were still relatively well-clothed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were still relatively clean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were still could change your shirt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But forget about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's-- that wasn't the problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then we prayed around the Sefer Torah all the prayers of the holidays.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
